			<p class="author"><img src="./styles/new-life/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" />by <strong>ghost_seregrail7</strong> on Tue Nov 18, 2008 6:59 pm </p>

			
			<div class="content">Massive game, with loads to see and do. I've hit about 55 hours and I've done all the major stuff. One problem is that there are quite a few bugs in the game, and it crashes a lot. It's still the best game I've played this year despite that and is easily my GOTY. Go buy it, it am good games! <img src="./images/smilies/old1.gif" alt=":old:" title="" /> <br /><br />Good:<br />Interesting<br />Great world to explore<br />Great Quests<br />VATS<br />Funny<br />Atmosphere<br /><br />Bad:<br />Voice acting<br />Buggy<br />Feels a little like a Oblivion mod<br /><br /><br />There's also a lot of mods starting to show up for it, just like with Oblivion.</div>

			
		</div>

